Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["FFTLog Redshift-Space Galaxy Master Integrals", "Title",ExpressionUUID->"67ade176-9f5a-4a5d-832b-fdece0d33d5b"],

Cell["\<\
This notebook closes the Gaussian matter-to-galaxy chain. The low-order \
line-of-sight master integrals are already established in the redshift-space \
matter notebook, so the focus here is the full Gaussian galaxy sector \
decomposition and its exact agreement with the local redshift-space kernel \
tables.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"b505ed51-4a94-49f2-97d3-0b03de0bd68d"],

